data.description: You found it! Gorgeous Richmond American home in quiet Fort Collins neighborhood that backs up to open space.  Enjoy the mountain views and access to walking paths that connect to Cooper Slough Natural Area and Rabbit Brush Park right from your back yard. Step inside to this gorgeous home and be greeted with soaring ceilings, double sided fireplace, and beautiful finishes throughout. You will love the wood grain porcelain tile in the kitchen and dining. Huge loft upstairs. This home is wired with whole house speakers and CAT5 & RG6 in every room. HOA includes non-potable water and garbage. New water heater 2023.  Priced for quick sale.  Don't miss this one!
